value: Resident, wetlands: scattered through all S of Sahara, Nile Delta area and Madagascar; rare or absent in forest area and NE and SW.
Locally in Africa, Madagascar, Oriental region and Australia
swamps, reedbeds, jheels, overgrown rice fields, mudy margins of pools, freshwater lakes with grassy islets, sewage ponds, mudflats overgrown with marsh grass
ground displays only, including displays on trees and bushes
